title: First Aid Educational Quiz

creator: Interlock Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Test your First Aid knowledge in this educational, fun, and challenging quiz game! Each question is presented in a random order, keeping you on your toes. Take the challenge and beat your friends!

The clock is ticking! Answer quickly and correctly to earn valuable bonus points. Speed is key – the faster your correct selection, the bigger the bonus. While you can take your time, bonus points are only awarded for swift responses.

Be the first to answer 50 questions correctly and claim victory over your friends!

Track your progress on the global leader board and see how you rank against players worldwide. Monitor your personal best score and your total cumulative score. Unlock achievements that give you bonus points.

Ready to prove you're a First Aid whiz? Challenge your friends and climb to the top of the leader boards!

This fun and entertaining game is perfect for learners of all ages!

Compete now and download for free!
